[04:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to keep reloading the page or even going back to history and all of these things and keep updating this omni reference. Luckily, we don\'t have to do that because, as I showed you the other week, they have added this chat interface that allows you to interact through text'

